data.description: Awesome Acworth Home For Sale!! This beautiful home is  conveniently located near the interstate and down town Acworth. This delightful home boasts a captivating exterior adorned with charming stone elements, ensuring exceptional curb appeal. Step inside to find an open-concept living room and kitchen, where high ceilings and a cozy fireplace create a welcoming atmosphere flooded with natural light. Upstairs, three bedrooms and two bathrooms provide the perfect retreat, while the lower level offers convenience with a half bath. Low quarterly HOA fee of just $180, which covers grass, bush, tree maintenance, and sprinkler system care, maintenance is a breeze. This meticulously landscaped property has recently undergone a transformation, with the installation of fresh sod by a professional landscaping company, ensuring the yard is in pristine condition and ready for its new owners. There are no rental restrictions in this community, offering both comfort and investment potential. Don't miss the chance to make this stunning Acworth property your own – schedule a viewing today and experience modern comfort in a tranquil neighborhood setting.
